          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 text-sm text-text-muted">
            Roles: Backend Engineer, Engineering Manager
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
          API server for taking audio data from edge nodes, applying business logic, and relaying instructions via Google DialogFlow. Used monorepo composed
