        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Javascript</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">NodeJS</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Firestore</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Google DialogFlow</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Google Cloud Platform</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Amazon Web Services</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Hashicorp Consul</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Docker Swarm</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Kubernetes</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Hashicorp Terraform</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">ElasticSearch</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Kibana</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">DataDog</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Gitlab CI</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Agile Development</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Wordpress Deployment -->
      <div class="bg-surface-light rounded-xl p-8 border border-white/10">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Wordpress Deployment</h3>
          <div class="flex gap-3 text-sm text-text-muted">
            Company: PUBG Corporation
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 text-sm text-text-muted">
            Roles: DevOps Engineer
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
          Deployed Wordpress to replace the company home page.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Amazon Web Services</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Hashicorp Terraform</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Car Rental Service -->
      <div class="bg-surface-light rounded-xl p-8 border border-white/10">
