          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
          Report using petabytes of game and infrastructure data to analyze if players had a meaningful win percentage increase when playing on a wired
          connection versus wireless connection.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Tableau</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">Hadoop Hive</span>
