        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
          Implemented green-field deployment of Splunk, aggregating all server logs, extracting metrics from logs, building alerts, and building dashboards in order to 
          reduce mean time to resolution (MTR) and increase success chance of root cause analysis (RCA).
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
